                        <interp inst="t18560818-name-272" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. These half crowns are both bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I gave the lady but one; I did not know it was bad; I am an unfortunate girl.</p>
